  "general_provisions": "This House rules resolution addresses disclosure requirements when a representative requests legislation.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This resolution:<hr><ltbullet>defines terms;<hr><ltbullet>when filing a request for legislation, allows a representative to indicate whether the representative filed the request for legislation at the request of an agency head; and<hr><ltbullet>makes technical and conforming changes.",
